				  <h4>The e-learning platform we are developing</h4>
				  <img style="border:0px" height="60px" src="assets/akademix-logo-svart.png">
				  <br><br>
				  <ul>
				    <li>Based on WeBWorK and Open EdX</li>
				    <li> Cloud-based and scalable (Amazon AWS)</li>
				    <li class="fragment grow"> Cross-institutional</li>
				  </ul>
				  <br><br>
				  <a href="http://beta.akademix.no">beta.akademix.no</a>
				</section>
