				<section>
				  <p> Long term ambition: </p>
				  <span style="color: blue; font-size:110%;"> Change the way we teach mathematics at HiB</span><br><br>
				  <div class="fragment">
				  <p> Courses consisting of three (interconnected) parts:</p>
				  <p>
				    <ul>
				      <li> Exercise sessions supported by video material </li>
				      <li> Computer labs </li>
				      <li> Overview lectures focusing on ideas, concepts and applications </li>
				    </ul>
				  </p>

